<title>CANADA: Moore to buy back up to 5 pct of shrs.</title>
<headline>Moore to buy back up to 5 pct of shrs.</headline>
<dateline>TORONTO 1997-06-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>Moore Corp said on Wednesday that it began a bid to buy back up to five million shares or 5.7 percent of its 88.3 million outstanding common shares.</p>
<p>The business forms company said the share repurchase would occur over the next 12 months through the Toronto and Montreal exchanges, at times and in numbers to be determined by Moore.</p>
<p>Moore said the program was intended to increase shareholder value and followed a previous buyback of 12 million shares that ended on May 30.</p>
<p>((Reuters Toronto Bureau 416 941-8100))</p>
